    <text>
        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>Sept 15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1853</date></p>
			<p>Dear Friend&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">I have waited <sic>untill</sic> I had<lb/> heard of <persName>Rehines</persName> safety&#44; ere I wrote for the<lb/> books&#44; he has left <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>&#44; at length&#44; and<lb/> is staying with <persName>Sarah Levy</persName>&#44; at the &#8220;<placeName>Bay of St Louis</placeName>&#8221;<lb/> thanks be to God&#44; my children&#44; have been spared<lb/> the dreadful scourge. You did not see <persName>Rosalie</persName><lb/> I suppose as they must have passed through<lb/> immediately&#44; since the arrived in <placeName>Baltimore</placeName><lb/> the same evening they left&#59; here&#59; imagine my delight<lb/> at her unexpected visit altho&#39; of short duration.<lb/> <persName>Augusts Block</persName>&#44; is still here&#44; perhaps you could<lb/> send the Books with his&#44; or by some opportunity<lb/> before the holy days&#8212;I will only take one <hi rend="underline">set</hi><lb/> of the smallest size and cheapest for <persName>Herman&#39;s</persName> use<lb/> if you recollect the two last <hi rend="underline">daily</hi> you sent me<lb/> I&#39;d like them to match as nearly as possible<lb/> I shall be obliged to have a daily with the<lb/> <hi rend="underline">set</hi> as I gave one of the others to <persName>Esther</persName>&#58; you&#39;ll<lb/> charge them with Bible to <persName>Rehine</persName>&#8212;</p>
			<p>When I can afford it I will have all &#8220;<persName>Grace<lb/> Aguillars</persName> works&#8221; at present must be satisfied<lb/> when I wrote you there was a prospect of better<lb/> times&#44; which has since taken flight&#8212;<persName>Mr Moses Jacob</persName>&#44;<lb/> I mean&#44; has a Son named to day a very fine<lb/> affair I&#39;m told&#44; <persName>Mrs Ottilingua</persName> is here.&#8212;</p>
			<p>Please mention me to my <persName>Aunt Grace</persName>&#44; I wish</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>I could see her here for the holy days&#44; say to<lb/> <persName role="author">Abby</persName> new house&#44; when I write her again&#44; I<lb/> shall get an answer I hope&#44; also remember me<lb/> to <persName>Mrs Florence</persName>&#44; and <persName>Miriam Spatts</persName>&#8212;<lb/> hope to see you soon remain as ever</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">your true friend</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">Abby Block</persName></p>
			<p>if an enquire of me give my<lb/> respects&#8212;Aunty is as usual.<lb/> please when you write again<lb/> let it be more <hi rend="underline">distinct</hi> I am<lb/> getting <hi rend="underline">old</hi>&#8212;</p>
		<pb n="3"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><hi rend="underline">Paid</hi></p>
			<p><hi rend="underline">To</hi></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi></placeName>.</p>
          
